newsitem.title: AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Past rate cut impact coming onstream-Costello.
newsitem.headline: RTRS-Past rate cut impact coming onstream-Costello.

text.p: Australian Treasurer Peter Costello said on Tuesday that the effects of past interest rate cuts were starting to be felt and were building.

"Interest rate cuts generally have a lag of 12 to 18 months What that means is that the impacts in relation to those interest rate cuts are coming onstream now and building," Costello told a Liberal Party luncheon.
